{"tid":1227923,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（好撚重要）五毛想將槍頭轉向消防！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-15T15:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T05:25:32.000Z","uid":15394,"like":1924,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":128,"replies":[{"pid":"f5f40b0bc8e36a15e45d0d1820fe79661f5c8947","tid":1227923,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:55:09.000Z","msg":"開始有post係到屌消防辦事不力，<br />\n質疑消防唔專業，唔救人，<br />\n氣墊唔推埋d (有欄杆block住呀仆街）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母玩分化！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n想用義士跳樓去改風向？<br />\n將茅頭指返消防，<br />\n等人轉移視線？<br />\n<br />\n消費義士，<br />\n我屌你老母臭西呀五毛狗！！！！"},{"pid":"814a82415a86e28a7d55880f6ab1cc44dcf0688c","tid":1227923,"uid":15394,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:55:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0caff0c1b4ba2dc230d070f351cb3873b062c37b","tid":1227923,"uid":15394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:56:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"935ca42c4c8ac19be0fd3c0cdb75cbc50b7b5adc","tid":1227923,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:57:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"270cd575abdad8be19bba3c2d5fe97ea546f9d5a","tid":1227923,"uid":10673,"like":316,"dislike":3,"score":313,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:57:33.000Z","msg":"消防員們 你地一直都係我最尊敬既人<br />\n<br />\n求下你地，下次再有人比警察打可唔可以黎幫下手<br />\n<br />\n我明白你地有包袱，但我相信唔會有人怪責你地企係警察同年輕人之間築防線（唔洗打人）<br />\n有你地係度唔會有人再用暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有一個人因為保護市民被炒我發誓我做鬼都唔放過你地上司"},{"pid":"dc4aed4bf4befb5a12ba01d0bcf9cd2ec5a7bd18","tid":1227923,"uid":15394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21bcc28e517649fa22ae3d11db890b3e8c628303","tid":1227923,"uid":91017,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:58:19.000Z","msg":"五毛都on9, 一振又吊法官, 醫生, 係唔係都吊一餐"},{"pid":"4728d303a2ede6faf99eaa3c76bf94cdf5a5fbe1","tid":1227923,"uid":93451,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n人地有良心過d 狗<br />\n你估佢地見到人死左好好過？<br />\n<br />\n阻一阻大家 為左防止d人比人利用 開左個po 提下大家<br />\n<br />\n岩岩琴日早上聖經個po 我發現到<br />\n一但上左熱門 就好容易比人操作到輿論<br />\n上左熱門好容易比人利用<br />\n因為好多人見到個po就咁like左就算 令一d 未有驗證 同未有討論既事 比人帶左風向<br />\n<br />\n所以開返下邊個po提下大家 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1220056/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1220056/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有時講錯左野就好容易比人利用<br />\n見到唔同既消息大家記得同周邊既朋友傾多啲<br />\n驗清楚真假 同諗清楚個樣野既後果<br />\n係而家信息過多既時間<br />\n思考係十分重要既一步<br />\n大家坐埋一條船 尊重係好重要既一樣野<br />\npushhh</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n上邊紅字係我覺得依幾日 時時刻mon po 既結論<br />\n如果大家諗完贊同可以去唔同po同地方share開去"},{"pid":"979824249c7c90a9067885a854b70ad73199e424","tid":1227923,"uid":15394,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:58:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n想用一晚時間黎改口風？"},{"pid":"c7fff791953396f204f1bfa349ae56852f1ebc44","tid":1227923,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:58:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5262b37b5caf0605639feb58e0871ca16128acd","tid":1227923,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:58:58.000Z","msg":"推你老母！"},{"pid":"339b6afa2af765fbac5317e25b6c6a91b2e1f82b","tid":1227923,"uid":257837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:59:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"684c70dc675368ad231d00501d73c6e882fd7b57","tid":1227923,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！！"},{"pid":"f36ca52eade90792cba0b735d3f58615f150c78f","tid":1227923,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:00:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a63d35c9c40b8f9deba7644a0c08f807a0358667","tid":1227923,"uid":164190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"debf10197177bf1bf0fdc8696f5e9b1e7f1f0650","tid":1227923,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:01:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c27d4c1d6375d05d122070a1c11425f7939e5f72","tid":1227923,"uid":64969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130543d626dcf24ddafc3491eea015c446aebd46","tid":1227923,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:02:47.000Z","msg":"要推 你老母"},{"pid":"51e6ea4f4705e1f7c11de145a56508bcdf5c90f1","tid":1227923,"uid":140738,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:02:53.000Z","msg":"係警察有問題<br />\n<br />\n警察用五個小時同佢傾<br />\n<br />\n但佢係反送中<br />\n<br />\n由其經過612之後<br />\n<br />\n佢仲點會相信警察<br />\n<br />\n而且仲要有警察帶盾"},{"pid":"4f7442f706fa1daa80753fc4eb5cb42214d74345","tid":1227923,"uid":202912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b77533a165f5c250804c05cb68611adda78e66a","tid":1227923,"uid":87394,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:02:58.000Z","msg":"On9 本身死左人就一定要檢討架啦<br />\n唔係話有人柒過你就可以抹消你既錯<br />\n仲要今次有晒片我諗冇乜人會認同佢地咁樣上去捉人掛？<br />\n條友呢個身型佢到底有咩自信可以捉得住佢？<br />\n仲要人地係自己行到呢步黎做威脅，唔係比人逼<br />\n一定唔會想你救，比你救左仲要比警察的去審一輪<br />\n失敗左就係一條人命唔係想話諗住搏一鋪呀？"},{"pid":"5a07b88bbf4cf950345f6deae76d3e8c9a30d636","tid":1227923,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:03:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fe0d69afc1a221d02d2002e7b9249babb2bc2175","tid":1227923,"uid":227984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:03:53.000Z","msg":"五毛狗全部不得好死<